# SKILL-ANDROID (P8 #293) — keystore placeholders.
#
# !!! CRITICAL: NEVER bake a real keystore path or password into this
# file. The values below are PLACEHOLDER NAMES that the `backend/
# codesign_store.py` (P3 #288) HSM layer populates at build time.
#
# Local dev may copy this to `keystore.properties` (gitignored) with
# real values — that file's gitignore entry is in the scaffold's
# `.gitignore` below. Production signing ALWAYS goes through
# `codesign_store.materialize_env()` which injects the OMNISIGHT_KEYSTORE_*
# env vars into the gradle process.
#
# The `app/build.gradle.kts` signing block reads in this order:
#   1. System env (`OMNISIGHT_KEYSTORE_PATH` etc.) — production
#   2. `keystore.properties` — local-dev / HIL testing
#   3. Empty — fails the release build fast (gradle error:
#      "keystore file not found"), which is the correct behaviour.

OMNISIGHT_KEYSTORE_PATH=$OMNISIGHT_KEYSTORE_PATH
OMNISIGHT_KEYSTORE_PASSWORD=$OMNISIGHT_KEYSTORE_PASSWORD
OMNISIGHT_KEY_ALIAS=$OMNISIGHT_KEY_ALIAS
OMNISIGHT_KEY_PASSWORD=$OMNISIGHT_KEY_PASSWORD
